room_title: Escape room "Unsinkable" by Rockwall Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: A wealthy survivor of the R.M.S. Titanic has created a beautiful golden replica of the ship to gift his rescuer. However, as the war outside his home forces him to leave with just the clothes on his back, he hides the statue somewhere in his city. He has left instructions for you to locate and uncover the replica and send it to his savior.
